{
  "stem": "27509.6",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We didn't have much with us in the form of luggage, and baggage, and so on.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The few things that we carried with us, they could have given us an hour's notice and we would have been gone.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But they gave us a very beautiful boat with a very nice trip from Japan to-- the modern, new boat.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was a holiday.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was a holiday trip on the upper deck.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We were sunning ourselves in the Pacific.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we arrived in Shanghai.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And that's how it happened.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The exact date-- there is a document.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We will find it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I've got an exact date.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I've got a document of landing in Shanghai.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "On our arrival Shanghai, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Shanghai had a-- two Jewish communities.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] They had a Vladivostok community of Russian Jews who lived there, excuse me, who were originally from [RUSSIAN] and came south down, because Shanghai was an open place.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And anybody could come and go.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They didn't have visas there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They were settled at the French concession, who lived in the French Concession.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And there was a Sephardi community of Baghdadi Jews amongst-- who came there as a result of this extraordinary success of the Sassoons and the [NON-ENGLISH], who became world famous starting from the Opium Wars in the 1840s, and so on, who amassed fortunes and so on.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then the people from-- from Baghdad started coming and claiming-- and claiming a relation status with those-- there were poor people and so on-- in such a way that there was quite a sizable Sephardi Jewish community.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But they were quite separate.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
